"    </li>",
"    <li class=\"plainItem\">",
"     <a class=\"medical medical_review\" href=\"UTD.htm?13/53/14168?source=related_link\">",
"      Overview of the complications of acute myeloid leukemia",
"     </a>",
"    </li>",
"    <li class=\"plainItem\">",
"     <a class=\"medical medical_review\" href=\"UTD.htm?7/56/8073?source=related_link\">",
"      Pathogenesis and etiology of disseminated intravascular coagulation",
"     </a>",
"    </li>",
"    <li class=\"plainItem\">",
"     <a class=\"medical medical_basics\" href=\"UTD.htm?0/62/994?source=related_link\">",
"      Patient information: Disseminated intravascular coagulation (The Basics)",
"     </a>",
"    </li>",
"    <li class=\"plainItem\">",
"     <a class=\"medical medical_review\" href=\"UTD.htm?0/52/841?source=related_link\">",
"      Protein C deficiency",
"     </a>",
"    </li>",
"    <li class=\"plainItem\">",
"     <a class=\"medical medical_review\" href=\"UTD.htm?13/2/13354?source=related_link\">",
"      Septic shock: Ongoing management after resuscitation in children",
